<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="DisableAbrtd" version="5.0">
 <title xml:id="SysMgmtServices">Disable Abrtd</title>
 <para>
  The abrtd daemon is used to generate information about processes that
  have crashed, and can expose sensitive information about the system.
  It is recommended that this service be disabled or removed.
 </para>
